title: ETH v1 Listing: Add AXS market
body:
Intro: This is a vote to list AXS on C.R.E.A.M. ETH v1 market with a Collateral Factor and Collateral Cap — contingent on decentralized oracle coverage.
 
Proposal: Listing Committee
 
Rational: Initiate GameFi coverage on C.R.E.A.M. markets. 
We are voting pre-oracle coverage, so we are able to launch an AXS market day 1 of oracle launch. 

For:
Add AXS market with Collateral Factor: 45% and Collateral Cap: $1M 

Against:
Do not make any changes to ETH v1 market.
author: 0x81f8CaBe89066d43EB4faFD8E4E5256C102E6E30
